(19, 19, '"Ficar" means "stay", but can also be used as "hook up with sb". But it doesn''''t necessarily means that you are getting laid.', '- Eae, como foi a festa ontem a noite?\n- Opa, fiquei com três!', 'gíria,pegar', 'A', 'bruno@tupilabs.com', '2012-08-26 21:09:29', '2012-08-26 21:09:29', 'kinow', ''),
