(22, 22, '"De boa" can be used as answer for "Beleza?". Or you can use it to refer to someone who is in a good situation.', '- [Véi], [cê] acha que ele vai repetir de ano?\n- Que nada, ele tá de boa.', 'gíria,suave,tranquilo', 'A', 'bruno@tupilabs.com', '2012-08-26 21:16:25', '2012-08-26 21:16:25', 'kinow', ''),
